―action area‖ means an area shown in any development plan or has 
been declared as such in accordance with the provisions of this Act to 
facilitate new development, redevelopment or improvement;

―amenities‖  means  such  quality  or  condition  of  a  place  or  area  as 
contributes  to  its  pleasantness,  harmony,  and  better  enjoyment,  and 
includes open spaces, parks, recreation grounds, and playgrounds;

―authorized officer‖, in  relation  to  any provision, means an officer 
designated  in  writing  by  the  Commissioner  to  be  an  authorized 
officer for the purposes of that provision;

(b)  any addition to or alteration of a building that affects or is 
